{"tid":1028784,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[苦主搜索] 90後大肚人魔，欠債唔還，借生仔賴皮，七宗罪","createTime":"2019-02-19T17:39:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T08:08:35.000Z","uid":193204,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8cc79c3bbbed71818fb2aa240cef56c03d464546","tid":1028784,"uid":193204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T17:39:52.000Z","msg":"<strong>\b<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">周\b端X ／周X嬋  七宗罪</span></span><br />\n</strong><div style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">1。唔熟唔七宗罪食，呃身邊識咗十幾年<strong>最好嘅朋友</strong><br />\n2。\b懷疑<strong>偽造文件</strong>，涉及刑事罪行<br />\n3。不斷講大話，死都唔肯還錢<br />\n4。<strong>呀伯積蓄都呃</strong>，祝佢生仔冇屎忽<br />\n5。身邊朋友幾乎個個比佢呃咗，正一掃把星<br />\n6。<strong>呃到朋友破產</strong>，人渣極品<br />\n7。扮晒純情小綿羊，實際係<strong>人魔</strong></span></span></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vvgWfFp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvvgWfFp.jpg&h=8d6c3d78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個\b周\b端X ／周X嬋係我朋友識咗十幾年嘅中學同學，竟然利用我朋友同佢之間嘅友情，設局呃我朋友同佢屋企人投資，total呃咗<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">\b170萬</span></span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n個騙局維持咗大約兩年，隻呀嬋聲稱可以幫我朋友投資，最初都係一，兩萬咁呃，而中間話投資有賺而比返錢\b我\b朋友，其後投資嘅金額就越嚟越來多，加上呀嬋一路都話投資係有賺錢嘅，我朋友就叫埋佢屋企人一齊投資，連我朋友爸爸都比隻呀嬋呃咗十幾萬，全部都係佢辛辛苦苦儲返嚟嘅血汗錢，咁就比個臭西呃咗。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>都係同另一位受害一樣，直到我朋友想拎返錢嘅時候，佢就諸多籍口，呀嬋就聲稱自己戶口比人凍結資產，但當我朋友要求佢交出\b銀行證明時候就話冇</strong></span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n其後，隻呀嬋更加癲到話可以再比錢去解凍自己戶口，又話自己冇credit card，就叫我朋友幫佢去比呢舊錢。而我朋友好\b想拎返啲本金就好傻豬豬咁幫咗佢。<br />\n<br />\n而佢同我朋友嘅對話中，亦有好多過數紀錄係呀嬋聲稱自己有過數，但我朋友係一毫子都收唔到，<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">因此我朋友懷疑呢啲轉帳紀錄亦係偽造嘅</span></span></strong>，目的就係成就呢宗騙案！而家隻呀嬋就痴L線到聲稱自己有千幾萬，只係戶口又被審查，所以冇辦法還錢。<br />\n<br />\n我朋友而家日日以淚洗臉，除咗怪責自己，仲要擔心點樣還嗰120萬卡數，今次真係比個呀嬋累死！！<br />\n<br />\n今次開POST，除咗要數晒呀嬋七宗罪所外，係要<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">希望大家小心此人，同埋想搵返之前都係比呀嬋呃咗160萬嗰位苦主出嚟</span></strong></span>。我唔知你係因為咩原因而del post，但對住呢啲仆街人魔唔應該心軟，要推到佢變過街老鼠為止。因為佢不單止呃咗你同我朋友，仲有唔少身邊朋友都比佢以投資\b名義去呃錢，有一個搵得萬五蚊嘅朋友，比佢搞到要每個月還二萬蚊，而負擔唔到就被迫<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">破產</span></span></strong>。咁仆街嘅人點都應該受返佢應得嘅懲罰！！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">周\b端X ／周X嬋 你唔好以為可以呃完人錢唔洗還，仲消遙法外！！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n之前有人開POST嘅CAP圖，唔知咩原因被DEL POST，但希望你可以<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">PM我，一齊對付呀嬋！</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kLVcysE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkLVcysE.jpg&h=0913ba52&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dd5672ef8a2850427d501aafa6b9fb62a4152c6a","tid":1028784,"uid":135278,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T18:09:14.000Z","msg":"見你朋友咁慘 幫你推下啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9d6e6ca85e7a12cfdbfd1ffaf6a5e0cfcb7b421","tid":1028784,"uid":90820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T18:24:56.000Z","msg":"報咗警未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6872071aa6c1ed94216773ef8e53695f16bde664","tid":1028784,"uid":193204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9d6e6ca85e7a12cfdbfd1ffaf6a5e0cfcb7b421","tid":1028784,"uid":90820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T18:24:56.000Z","msg":"報咗警未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T18:29:52.000Z","msg":"警已報<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但話要時間去查，而家好似未夠料住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8293ef20d7ea956c7ba9e1d22c9511bc75fdec9","tid":1028784,"uid":109416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T01:02:30.000Z","msg":"你唔貪點會比人呃到。"},{"pid":"f521a301e5e248fff7511abda118a8f0409faceb","tid":1028784,"uid":175622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T01:04:25.000Z","msg":"幫你推"},{"pid":"5d7b10650570106b1d08bcc030e5c9c258785e8b","tid":1028784,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T01:05:36.000Z","msg":"龐氏騙局 估唔到仲work<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c36c793ddf79d133aa9d3df72ff669b28f764b8","tid":1028784,"uid":134128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T01:51:18.000Z","msg":"咁小相"},{"pid":"4463831a40903c2a1221f7a55579a988fa4e4e43","tid":1028784,"uid":22232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T14:04:42.000Z","msg":"岩岩見到個post,我朋友都出事😰 加佢telegram : mrvic123,thanks"},{"pid":"be5ee54c359298150a592d0957233f05726a5b1f","tid":1028784,"uid":193204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4463831a40903c2a1221f7a55579a988fa4e4e43","tid":1028784,"uid":22232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T14:04:42.000Z","msg":"岩岩見到個post,我朋友都出事😰 加佢telegram : mrvic123,thanks"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T08:08:35.000Z","msg":"tg加咗佢！"}]}